This is the implementation of PhoneGap for Windows Phone 7 that is the furthest along (https://github.com/phonegap/phonegap-wp7).

While there are still lots of issues this does show a lot of functionality working. The current status is:

ACCELEROMETER: partly
CAMERA: partly
COMPASS: no
CONTACTS: no
FILE: no
GEOLOCATION: partly
MEDIA: no
NETWORK: yes
NOTIFICATION (ALERT): yes
NOTIFICATION (SOUND): yes
NOTIFICATION (VIBRATION): yes
STORAGE: no
SMS: yes (trigger request to compose)
Telephony : yes (trigger request to make a call)

In order to contribute to this project, you must sign and submit the Contributor License Agreement: http://www.phonegap.com/contributor-agreement/